\par {\ltrch\loch\f1 \tab Having received advice from a calligrapher and illuminator of note, I am planning to make a larger version of this ruler, since our scrolls tend to be larger than period manuscripts tended to be, and to be divided less often into two columns that could be
 ruled separately.}
